quran[27]{c,v,t}:
  55,68,"Hino e majji : muuyantee…ói, e le…ó…óe tamarooje e rummaana."
  55,69,"E ko hol…ói e ne'emaaji Joomi mon …óin njeddoton?"
  55,70,"Hino e …óiin …ói…ói : rew…ďe su…ďaa…ďe (labaa…ďe)."
  55,71,"E ko hol…ói e ne'emaaji Joomi mon …óin njeddoton?"
  55,72,"huurul'aynii…ďe(yaaja gite), soomaa…ďe e tillisooji,"
  55,73,"E ko hol…ói e ne'emaaji Joomi mon …óin njeddoton?"
  55,74,"ne…ó…óo memaani …ďen ado ma…ď…ďe, wonaa kadi jinna."
  55,75,"E ko hol…ói e neemaaji Joomi mon …óin njeddoton?"
  55,76,"Ko …ďe so…ď…ďindotoo…ďe e dow ngawluuji haakooji, e nda…ó…óule abqari labaa…óe."
  55,77,"E ko hol…ói e ne'emaaji Joomi mon …óin njeddoton?"
  55,78,"Barkinii innde Jooma nden, Jom mawngu e teddungal !"
  56,1,"Si ko darotoongal ngal dariima,"
  56,2,"alanaa daragol maggal ngol pennoowo."
  56,3,"Koyfin…óinatngal (yeddu…ďe), …ďamtatngal (goo…óii…ďe)."
  56,4,"Si lesdi ndiin dilliniraama dillannde,"
  56,5,"pelle …óeen munciroyee muncannde,"
  56,6,"…óe ngonta collaari ruuynatndi,"
  56,7,"Mbattinon nooneeji tati :"
  56,8,"Ko wontiroo…ďe √Īaamo …ďeen - iskin …ďeen yim…ďe √Īaamo !"
  56,9,"e wontiroo…ďe nano …ďeen, bis e …ďeen yim…ďe nano !"
  56,10,"Ko adondiratnoo…ďe …ďeen (e mo∆ī∆īere ka aduna), adoytee (naatneede Aljanna)."
  56,11,"Ko …ďeen ngoni badnitaa…ďe …ďeen."
  56,12,"ka Aljannaaji ne'eminii…ói,"
  56,13,"dental jeyaangal e [mofte] adinoo…ďe …ďeen,"
  56,14,"e see…óaa…ďe jiyaa…ďe e [mofte] sakkitii…ďe …ďeen,"
  56,15,"he…ďe e hoore dan…óe yu…ď…ďiraa…óe [kaŇčŇče],"
  56,16,"hara he…ďe so…ď…ďindii e majje, feewtondir…ďe."